Economic Freedom Fighters leader Julius Malema sent words
of warning to president Cyril Ramaphosa and DA leader Mmusi Maimane during the
debate on SONA in the National Assembly on Monday.Malema was responding to Maimane and Ramaphosa on the
issue of expropriation of land without compensation. During SONA on Friday last week, Ramaphosa promised the ANC will go ahead with
